ies, campaigns, Hajj, or \u2018Umrah, he would exalt Allah three times at the top of every hill or plateau. Then, the Prophet would say, \u201cThere is no God but Allah alone,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/02\/28\/make-me-partner-with-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15463,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: You make me a partner with Allah?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cWhat Allah wills and what you will.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHave you made me a partner with Allah? Rather, what Allah wills alone.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 783 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26465,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/28\/prophet-prohibits-social-isolation\/","url_meta":{"origin":15463,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Loneliness: The Prophet forbids total social isolation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 28, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited isolation, that a man spend the night alone or travel alone. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 5650 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir Al-Tabari said, \u201cThis is discouragement in the form of discipline and guidance, as it is feared\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":722,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/23\/believer-not-stung-twice\/","url_meta":{"origin":15463,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Lessons: Believers learn from bad experiences","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believer is not stung twice from the same hole.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6133, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2998 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25901,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/05\/dua-wake-up-in-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":15463,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication to say when waking up in night","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever wakes up in the night and says, 'There is no God but Allah, alone without any partner. To Him belong the dominion and all praise, and He has power over all things. All praise is due\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3239,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/19\/isa-abd-allah-ruh-maryam\/","url_meta":{"origin":15463,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Eisa: Whoever testifies that Jesus is the servant of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever testifies that there is no God but Allah alone without any partners, that Muhammad is His servant and His Messenger, that Jesus is the servant of Allah and His Messenger, His word which He\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15463","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias